description:
President Trump joins Clay and Buck from Trump National Golf Club Bedminster to discuss the economy, Dr. Fauci, the upcoming Midterms and much more. Senator Rand Paul calls into the show to discuss how he plans to hold Dr. Anthony Fauci accountable for his covid sins.
